00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:14,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's all thanks to the fairies.</font>

255
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:17,770
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They protect our flowers.</font>

256
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:20,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I want more food!</font>

257
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:23,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If you have enough energy left to shout, then you're fine.</font>

258
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:28,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We may be poor, but this country is free from war.</font>

259
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:31,880
