00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">To everyone in Dressrosa.</font>

324
00:23:50,610 --> 00:23:51,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">King Riku!</font>

325
00:23:51,710 --> 00:23:53,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's King Riku!</font>

326
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:58,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I have a request. It's rather sudden, and so unreasonable you might doubt your hearing, but...</font>

