328
00:24:02,980 --> 00:24:05,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please just get whatever money you have...</font>

329
00:24:05,250 --> 00:24:07,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">and lend it all to me! {Xemnas: nuance and all}</font>

